snippet.title: Best VGM 2214 - Silent Hill 4 - Nightmarish Waltz
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1751 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OUmeK282f-E

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS2 / Xbox / PC
Silent Hill 4: The Room (2004)
Nightmarish Waltz
Akira Yamaoka
